      <title>[인사] 국무조정실·국무총리비서실 외</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/09/14/5OFZSGPS5ZEIDNAYHC363ZCOSA/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/09/14/5OFZSGPS5ZEIDNAYHC363ZCOSA/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
      <description/>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 16:33:35 +0000</pubDate>
